Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.49,0:04:39.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,Not many people can go backwards on a skateboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.49,0:04:39.94,CHN,,0,0,0,,没几个人能倒着滑滑板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.29,0:04:43.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,How did you get the idea for a robot that will skateboard?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.29,0:04:43.64,CHN,,0,0,0,,会滑滑板的机器人这个点子 你们是怎么想出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.64,0:04:46.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Should I say the truth or make a nice story?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.64,0:04:46.47,CHN,,0,0,0,,要实打实讲还是听故事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:47.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,- [Derek] Tell us the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:47.60,CHN,,0,0,0,,那就说事实吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:50.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yeah, so we went hiking and we saw
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:50.07,CHN,,0,0,0,,我们在一次徒步旅行的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.07,0:04:53.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,about 10 people going down the mountain on a skateboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.07,0:04:53.69,CHN,,0,0,0,,然后看到有大概十个人滑滑板下山
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.69,0:04:55.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,And then we thought, wow, this is really cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.69,0:04:55.26,CHN,,0,0,0,,然后我们就想 哇这也太酷了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.26,0:04:58.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,What if we try our robots to make it do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.26,0:04:58.19,CHN,,0,0,0,,要不让我们的机器人也这么玩 怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:05:01.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,So we went to the first shop and we bought a skateboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:05:01.63,CHN,,0,0,0,,然后我们就去附近的商店买了个滑板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.63,0:05:04.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,We modified it and we tried it and it worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.63,0:05:04.32,CHN,,0,0,0,,然后我们改进了小里欧 试了试 还真的可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:05.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,- [Derek] So do you think it allows the robot
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:05.47,CHN,,0,0,0,,那么你们是觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.47,0:05:08.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,to save energy by riding on a skateboard?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.47,0:05:08.09,CHN,,0,0,0,,让机器人滑滑板可以节省能量？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.09,0:05:11.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,- It's more efficient because it uses the legs less.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.09,0:05:11.58,CHN,,0,0,0,,滑滑板的效率更高 因为不需要频繁用腿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:13.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,The legs are basically used to steer,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:13.31,CHN,,0,0,0,,腿就是用来转向的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.31,0:05:15.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,and then it's just the propellors
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.31,0:05:15.09,CHN,,0,0,0,,螺旋桨才是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.09,0:05:17.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,that are used to accelerate the skateboard
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.09,0:05:17.06,CHN,,0,0,0,,用来加速滑板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.06,0:05:17.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,forward and backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.06,0:05:17.90,CHN,,0,0,0,,前后移动的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:21.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,So yeah, it makes it save a bit more energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:21.19,CHN,,0,0,0,,总的来说，它确实可以节省一些能量的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.19,0:05:23.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,- The propellors of course, make it possible
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.19,0:05:23.15,CHN,,0,0,0,,- 那组螺旋桨确实可以让它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.15,0:05:24.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,to skateboard backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.15,0:05:24.70,CHN,,0,0,0,,倒着滑滑板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.70,0:05:27.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,Something I struggled with.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.70,0:05:27.12,CHN,,0,0,0,,这我拼命也学不会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.12,0:05:29.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,It definitely would help if I had a propeller.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.12,0:05:29.89,CHN,,0,0,0,,但我戴上一副螺旋桨说不定就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.76,0:05:36.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,But the real challenge was slacklining.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.76,0:05:36.76,CHN,,0,0,0,,但真正的挑战还是走钢丝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.46,0:05:45.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,This looks incredibly unstable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.46,0:05:45.45,CHN,,0,0,0,,这绳子看着很晃悠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.45,0:05:48.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,So I think this proves the point of just like,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.45,0:05:48.47,CHN,,0,0,0,,所以我想这个印证了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:50.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,how important control systems are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:50.61,CHN,,0,0,0,,所谓姿态控制的重要性
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.61,0:05:53.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,You can tell from the footage I have no idea what I'm doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.61,0:05:53.85,CHN,,0,0,0,,看这段视频你就知道我啥也不会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.74,0:05:59.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,All right, I thought I would be slightly better at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.74,0:05:59.57,CHN,,0,0,0,,好吧，我以为我还至少能比这好点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.57,0:06:00.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let's give it another shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.57,0:06:00.92,CHN,,0,0,0,,再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.24,0:06:03.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.24,0:06:03.07,CHN,,0,0,0,,好的，再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.81,0:06:06.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,Can anyone slackline?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.81,0:06:06.37,CHN,,0,0,0,,有人会走钢丝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:13.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:13.07,CHN,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.07,0:06:14.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.07,0:06:14.50,CHN,,0,0,0,,这也太难了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.50,0:06:16.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,I need a robot to do this for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.50,0:06:16.73,CHN,,0,0,0,,看来得需要一个机器人来替我做这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.26,0:06:32.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,I like the sidestepping technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.26,0:06:32.38,CHN,,0,0,0,,我觉得侧步走挺不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.26,0:06:35.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should have been doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.26,0:06:35.06,CHN,,0,0,0,,当时我就改侧着走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.78,0:06:39.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,Kind of like copy his technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.78,0:06:39.38,CHN,,0,0,0,,借鉴一下它的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.47,0:06:48.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,I tried to get some tips by watching Leonardo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.47,0:06:48.69,CHN,,0,0,0,,看着里奥走钢丝我想我得到了些提示
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:57.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,But improvement was negligible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:57.33,CHN,,0,0,0,,但结果还是提升不大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:03.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,I should've prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:03.03,CHN,,0,0,0,,我应该提早准备的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:06.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,You might think it's cheating to use propellers,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:06.61,CHN,,0,0,0,,你可能会觉得机器人在利用螺旋桨走后门
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:09.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,but the robot is clearly not flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:09.35,CHN,,0,0,0,,但是它确实没在飞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.35,0:07:11.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,It is supporting itself mostly using the rope,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.35,0:07:11.87,CHN,,0,0,0,,它用绳子做支撑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.87,0:07:13.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,and it's able to stabilize itself
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.87,0:07:13.87,CHN,,0,0,0,,而且在这么晃的绳子上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:15.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,even with the wild bouncing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:15.58,CHN,,0,0,0,,都能保持平稳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.14,0:07:18.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,- So human professional slack liner,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.14,0:07:18.89,CHN,,0,0,0,,对于专业的走绳表演者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:20.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,you can see some of their videos,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:20.85,CHN,,0,0,0,,你会发现他们在视频中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.85,0:07:22.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,actually they use arms stretched
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.85,0:07:22.66,CHN,,0,0,0,,会把手臂展平
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.66,0:07:24.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,and then they can balance themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.66,0:07:24.64,CHN,,0,0,0,,以维持平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.64,0:07:27.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,We don't have the arms for LEO yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.64,0:07:27.10,CHN,,0,0,0,,我们还没给里奥安装两臂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.10,0:07:29.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,We are planning to add a manipulation
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.10,0:07:29.22,CHN,,0,0,0,,我们打算为它安装机械臂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.22,0:07:31.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,so that he can actually carry some object.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.22,0:07:31.63,CHN,,0,0,0,,这样它就能拿点什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.63,0:07:34.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,But in the meantime, we are using the propellers
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.63,0:07:34.10,CHN,,0,0,0,,而目前我们在用螺旋桨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:38.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,to stabilize LEO while he's actually walking on a slackline.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:38.12,CHN,,0,0,0,,让里奥在走绳时保持稳定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:40.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,- It's funny because like the robot feels like
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:40.96,CHN,,0,0,0,,这些机器人行走或飞行的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.96,0:07:42.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,it's got kind of a personality to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.96,0:07:42.43,CHN,,0,0,0,,好像通人性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.43,0:07:45.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,The way it walks and flies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.43,0:07:45.26,CHN,,0,0,0,,这挺有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.26,0:07:47.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's just totally something you're not used to seeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.26,0:07:47.70,CHN,,0,0,0,,这仅仅是你还不习惯所见的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.70,0:07:48.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,- It looks natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.70,0:07:48.68,CHN,,0,0,0,,它看起来很自然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.68,0:07:51.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,Actually, I have to say that the sensors
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.68,0:07:51.10,CHN,,0,0,0,,实际上 这些传感器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.10,0:07:53.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,are sampled at 1,000 times per second,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.10,0:07:53.50,CHN,,0,0,0,,每秒采样 1000 次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.50,0:07:56.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,but the controller is actually being recomputed
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.50,0:07:56.66,CHN,,0,0,0,,但是无论传输什么信号
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:58.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,whatever signal you are sending
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:58.16,CHN,,0,0,0,,螺旋桨和腿关节的控制系统
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:08:01.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,to propellers and the leg joints is 200 times per second.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:08:01.84,CHN,,0,0,0,,每秒计算 200 次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.84,0:08:04.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,So it's pretty fast computation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.84,0:08:04.35,CHN,,0,0,0,,所以说它其实算得很快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.35,0:08:07.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,- [Derek] 200 times a second it is adjusting what it's doing
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.35,0:08:07.65,CHN,,0,0,0,,它用每秒 200 次的频率规划动作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.65,0:08:08.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,to maintain balance?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.65,0:08:08.58,CHN,,0,0,0,,来保持平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.58,0:08:11.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yes, especially propeller control signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.58,0:08:11.02,CHN,,0,0,0,,是的 特别是螺旋桨的控制信号
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.02,0:08:13.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,- How does that compare to humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.02,0:08:13.03,CHN,,0,0,0,,与人类相比如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.03,0:08:14.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Oh, humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.03,0:08:14.28,CHN,,0,0,0,,呵 人类
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.28,0:08:17.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,So humans can do very sophisticated tasks,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.28,0:08:17.44,CHN,,0,0,0,,人类能够胜任相当繁杂的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.44,0:08:21.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,but in terms of a fast reaction, it's a very crude machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.44,0:08:21.21,CHN,,0,0,0,,但是在快速反应这方面 人类并不是那么精密的机器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.21,0:08:25.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,So humans, overall, has a few seconds of delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.21,0:08:25.49,CHN,,0,0,0,,总体而言 人类反应会有数秒的延迟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.49,0:08:26.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,Time delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.49,0:08:26.33,CHN,,0,0,0,,在时间上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:28.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Is this why I was struggling on the slackline?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:28.19,CHN,,0,0,0,,这是我在扁带上挣扎的原因吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:30.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Maybe, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:30.27,CHN,,0,0,0,,也许 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.27,0:08:32.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,- [Derek] How do you feel about the performance here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.27,0:08:32.43,CHN,,0,0,0,,你觉得今天表现它如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.43,0:08:33.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yeah, I think it beat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.43,0:08:33.64,CHN,,0,0,0,,是的 我觉得它比你强
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.11,0:08:36.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I mean, not that that's hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.11,0:08:36.50,CHN,,0,0,0,,我不是说那个 走绳很难
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.50,0:08:38.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,but this is very impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.50,0:08:38.38,CHN,,0,0,0,,但它的表现让人印象深刻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.38,0:08:41.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,If you imagine a robot like LEONARDO in the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.38,0:08:41.30,CHN,,0,0,0,,想象一下未来像这样的机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.30,0:08:44.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,like the greatest LEONARDO you could make,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.30,0:08:44.28,CHN,,0,0,0,,比方说能造出最大的里奥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.28,0:08:48.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,what woluld that robot look like and do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.28,0:08:48.16,CHN,,0,0,0,,它会长什么样 它能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.16,0:08:51.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,- So definitely having a LEO-like robot in space,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.16,0:08:51.89,CHN,,0,0,0,,如果把像里奥这样的机器人部署在太空
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:53.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,that would be amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:53.37,CHN,,0,0,0,,一定非常炫酷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.37,0:08:55.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,But of course, depending on where you go,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.37,0:08:55.42,CHN,,0,0,0,,但是当然 取决于工作环境
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.42,0:08:57.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,you might not be able to use propellers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.42,0:08:57.08,CHN,,0,0,0,,螺旋桨可能派不上用场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.08,0:08:59.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,So then you would need to use thrusters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.08,0:08:59.66,CHN,,0,0,0,,这样就得用推进器了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.66,0:09:00.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,- So eventually, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.66,0:09:00.49,CHN,,0,0,0,,所以 最后 的确
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.49,0:09:04.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,We want to develop this leg-based adaptive landing gear,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.49,0:09:04.57,CHN,,0,0,0,,我们想要开发这种基于机械腿的自适应着陆装置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.57,0:09:07.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,and then we give that to next generation Mars helicopter,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.57,0:09:07.56,CHN,,0,0,0,,然后我们会把它用于下一代火星直升机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:10.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,or next generation flying cars
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:10.26,CHN,,0,0,0,,或是次世代飞行汽车
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.26,0:09:14.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,so that it can actually land in very challenging conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.26,0:09:14.56,CHN,,0,0,0,,它能在极具挑战性的环境中着陆
